# BioAT
the Bioinformatic Analysis Tools
## About bioat
Bref:  <u>**bioat**, a python **package** & **command line toolkit** for Bioinformatics and data science!</u>

Home: https://github.com/hermanzhaozzzz/bioat

License: Apache-2.0

